      • getNodes

        public java.util.ArrayList<GNode> getNodes()
        Redefines getNodes() implementation og GGraph, which simply returns the ArrayList of its nodes. Here we get a new ArrayList Object with all nodes from each included GGraphTile plus additionally the nodes that were created due to connecting neighbour GGraphTile instances, plus the additional overlay nodes from approaches for start and end point of a routing access.
        Overrides:
        getNodes in class GGraph
        Returns:
        all node ot the multi graph
